<li>Thinking of you and your family during this difficult time.</li>
<li>Sending you strength and peace as you grieve.</li>
<li>With heartfelt sympathy, we share in your sorrow.</li>
<li>May your memories bring you comfort.</li>
<li>We are so sorry for your loss.  Our thoughts are with you.</li>
<li>Words cannot express our sorrow.  You're in our prayers.</li>
